Company Overview of Energy XXI Leasehold, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Energy XXI Leasehold, LLC was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Houston, Texas. The company operates as a subsidiary of Energy XXI Gulf Coast, Inc.


1021 Main StreetSuite 2626Houston, TX 77002United StatesFounded in 2011



Phone: (713) 351-3000








